{"tid":2448994,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK Spotify 追蹤人數破兩千萬　創全球女團新紀錄！","createTime":"2021-03-16T10:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T11:29:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"90f04cbb0977094c7aed97b0973e655d3d9ca40c","tid":2448994,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_ed4fc8c18372d9f5dacc7de4d69b301f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-16/134296-900271.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_ed4fc8c18372d9f5dacc7de4d69b301f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-16%2F134296-900271.png&h=2b82f7b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK 除了不斷以 MV 觀看次數締造新紀錄外，在串流音樂平台 Spotify 上的人氣也很驚人！<br />\n<br />\n在美國時間 15 日時，BLACKPINK 在 Spotify 上的追蹤人數突破了 2000 萬人，不僅寫下前全世界女團的新紀錄，也緊追在 Ariana Grande、Rihanna、Dua Lipa⋯⋯等巨星之後。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_110e16585557ef7e190a7de5058f89df/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-16/134296-900272.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_110e16585557ef7e190a7de5058f89df%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-16%2F134296-900272.jpeg&h=7072c8e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早在 2019 年便成為 Sportify 上最強女團的 BLACKPINK，在最近一年來追蹤人數翻倍成長，同時也在 YouTube 上接連創造紀錄，顯現出她們在串流時代通殺影、音平台的強大威力。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，成員 Ros&eacute; 最近推出的個人單曲〈R〉也獲得了好成績，主打歌 &ldquo;On the Ground&rdquo; 不僅橫掃 51 國 iTunes 熱門歌曲榜，也在 Spotify 上寫下韓國個人女歌手 24 小時內的播放次數新高。<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment）"},{"pid":"fe39c74bd7ddffeb888c2e835166a3e6d40b575a","tid":2448994,"uid":274500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"The biggest girl group in the world<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840694587a15cc3a8d5003e87637c814ca04bd6e","tid":2448994,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:29:17.000Z"